# Military Reformation

Seeing the lack of our militaries capabilities, our forces will go under an extensive 30 week training program, from Weapons practice to guerilla warfare while also having 3 weeks of combined arms training.

Our tank crews will be trained extensively for 24 weeks using our most up to date tank the T-12-76 utilising accuracy, discovering weakspots but also spotting of enemy armour and vehicles, they will also be trained on how to utilise speed and brute force to crush their opponents via outflanking.

Our pilots will have atleast 1500 hours of air time a year, practicing using our Qin Tsung aircraft being trained to effectively utilise the strengths of the aircraft as well as developing cohesion within squadrons via training programs and team work skills.
